T1  - Relationship banking and firms’ earnings quality – Does it matter whether banks are creditors or owners?
AU  - Bigus, Jochen
AU  - Weicker, Marina
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 159
SP  - 107050
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/02/01/
